reviewText: Really enjoyable quick workout that really makes you sweat!!!
I've had it for years but I still use it. I make the workouts a little harder for myself now, but that's easy enough to do by adding more punches and kicks, and by using hand weights intermittently.
Good tape for when you are short on time.
Great workout video and easy to follow. Even though its only 30 mins combined, it keeps you moving and feeling energized.
great product! If you are short on time & want an all over workout  this is it.
